
                       geant4-10-05-ref-01
                       ===================

Major development/fixes included since the last development tag are:

 o Allowing absolute zero proper decay time.
 o G4EmStandardPhysics_option4: changed RangeFactor to 0.08 to improve
   results from fanoCavity.
 o Fixed (weak and strong) event non-reproducibility in INCLXX.
 o Cross-sections: added high energy extension of nu-e xsc (M_W and M_Z
   propagator factors and Glashow resonance).
 o Added new visualization UI commands for view interpolation and centering.

---------- Reference-tag 'Release Notes' -----------

(+)  Fixes included in release 10.4.p03
(o)  Fixes included in release 10.5.p01

Summarised, the list of changes is the following:

cmake                                            cmake-V10-05-00             (o)
-----
- Added configuration GEANT4_USE_SMARTSTACK to enable use of smart-stack
  algorithm for default stack in G4TrackStack.

digits_hits                                      digits_hits-V10-05-00       (o)
-----------
- Fixed shadowing compilation warning in G4ScoringBox and G4ScoringCylinder.

event                                            event-V10-05-01             (o)
-----
- G4PrimaryTransformer: allowing absolute zero proper decay time.
- G4HEPEvtInterface: clean up G4Exception severities when end-of-file
  is detected.

g3tog4                                           g3tog4-V10-05-00            (o)
------
- Fixed shadowing compilation warning in G3toG4MakeSolid.

geometry
--------
- management (geommng-V10-05-00)                                             (o)
  o Use reverse_iterator in G4SolidStore::DeRegister() in order to speedup   (+)
    partial deregistration on setups with many solids instances.
  o G4Region: added possibility to disable search in the tree in             (+)
    AddRootLogicalVolume() for speeding up process in complex flat geometries.
- solids/specific (geom-specific-V10-05-01):                                 (o)
  o Disabled precise computation of extent and use simple bounding-box in
    CalculateExtent() for G4Tet and G4TessellatedSolid, to speed up
    intialisation in setups with relatively complex meshes.
  o Apply bounding-box calculation for extent also for the corresponding
    VecGeom wrappers.

global                                           global-V10-05-00            (o)
------
- Updated date and tag-ID for ref-01

graphics_reps                                    greps-V10-05-00
-------------
- G4VisExtent: added operator*(const G4Transform3D&).

particles                                        particles-V10-05-00         (o)
---------
- G4PrimaryParticle: allowing absolute zero proper decay time.

persistency/ascii                                ascii-V10-05-00             (o)
-----------------
- Fixed shadowing compilation warning in G4tgbGeometryDumper and G4tgbVolume.

physics_lists/constructors/electromagnetic       phys-ctor-em-V10-05-02      (o)
------------------------------------------
- G4EmStandardPhysicsWVI: use G4eplusTo2GammaOKVIModel with 3-gamma
  annihilation for e+.
- G4EmStandardPhysics_option4: changed RangeFactor to 0.08 to improve results
  from fanoCavity test.
- G4EmModelActivator: fixed compilation warning on clang.

processes/decay                                  decay-V10-05-00             (o)
---------------
- G4Decay, G4UnknownDecay: allowing absolute zero proper decay time.

processes/electromagnetic/dna                    emdna-V10-05-01
-----------------------------
- Moved checking of position of track status in
  G4ITStepProcessor::SetInitialStep().
- Clarified pointer ownership in G4DNAChemistryManager.

processes/electromagnetic/standard               emstand-V10-05-00           (o)
----------------------------------
- G4eplusTo2GammaOKVIModel: fixed crash at initialisation.

processes/hadronic
------------------
- cross_sections (hadr-cross-V10-05-01)
  o G4NeutrinoElectronNcXsc, G4NeutrinoElectronTotXsc: high energy extension
    of nu-e xsc (M_W and M_Z propagator factors and Glashow resonance).
  o G4ChipsNeutronElasticXS: fixed compilation warnings on clang.            (o)
- models/de_excitation (hadr-deex-V10-05-00)                                 (o)
  o G4LevelReader: fixed typo. Addressing problem report #2124.
- models/inclxx (hadr-inclxx-V10-05-00)                                      (o)
  o G4INCLHFB: fixed (weak and strong) event non-reproducibility by making
    the arrays 'radiusP, radiusN, diffusenessP, diffusenessN' thread-local.
- models/radioactive_decay (radioactive_decay-V10-05-00)
  o G4RadioactiveDecayBase: added StreamInfo() method; updated to new
    N shell EC; enable printout of parameters with G4VERBOSE in
    BuildPhysicsTable().

visualization                                    vis-V10-05-06
-------------
- management:
  o Include parameterised volumes in overlap checking and visualisation
    in G4LogicalVolumeModel (in addition to ordinary placements).
  o Introduced "/vis/viewer/centreOn" and "/vis/touchable/centreOn" UI commands.
    This allows one to centre the view (zoom in) on a volume.
    Reset with "/vis/viewer/reset".
  o Rationalised view interpolation; encapsulate algorithm into base class
    G4VVisCommand, so that commands "/vis/viewer/interpolate",
    "/vis/viewer/centreOn" and "/vis/touchable/centerOn" now use this.
    Might consider use by all view changing commands.
  o Pick up default number of line-segments-per-circle from G4Polyhedron.    (o)
  o Improved guidance for "/vis/scene/add/volume".
  o Minor improvements to visualization manager.
- modeling:
  o Added volume count (but commented out printing).
- gMocren:                                                                   (o)
  o Fixed shadowing compilation warning in G4GMocrenFileSceneHandler.

examples                                         examples-V10-05-01
--------
- Updated documentation and reference outputs.
- advanced/doiPET (doiPET-V10-05-00)                                         (o)
  o Fixed compilation warnings on clang for unused data members in
    doiPETDetectorConstruction and doiPETEventAction classes.
- extended/electromagnetic/TestEm5 (testem5-V10-05-00)
  o StackinAction: fixed log histograms, which where filled in a wrong way.
  o PhysListEm19DStandard: use 3-gamma annihilation model.
- extended/hadronic/Hadr01 (exhadr01-V10-05-00)
  o HistoManager: added linear histogram for pion energy at production.
- extended/hadronic/Hadr02 (exhadr02-V10-05-00)                              (o)
  o Fixed bug in the energe range of the transition between FTFP and BERT
    for the recently created CRMC_FTFP_BERT physics list.
- extended/medical/dna/dnaphysics (dnaphysics-V10-05-00)                     (o)
  o Updated README.
- extended/medical/fanoCavity (fano-V10-05-00)
  o DetectorConstruction, DetectorMessenger: fixed usage of base materials
    and cleanup (should fix ~1% error for Opt4 EM physics)
- extended/runAndEvent/RE05 (exampleRE05-V10-05-00)                          (o)
  o Reduced the number of events in pythia_event.data to make it smaller than
    2 MB. Number of events executed by the macro exampleRE05.in is also reduced
    accordingly.

