- Updated reference outputs and tools.
- tests/test19 (test19-V10-05-00)
  o Test19Histo: fixed g++ 8.2 warnings.
- tests/test22 (test22-V10-05-00)
  o Updated subdirectory  PbarPchan/ and added the new one PbarHyperonV/ 
    for the validation of FTF antiproton annihilation.
- tests/test23 (test23-V10-05-01)
  o Tst23Histo, TstHisto: fixed g++ 8.2 warnings.
- tests/test47 (test47-V10-05-00)
  o HistoTest47: fixed g++ 8.2 warnings.
- tests/test48 (test48-V10-05-00)
  o TestStoppingHisto: fixed g++ 8.2 warnings.
- tests/test67 (test67-V10-05-00)
  o Calculate the mean number of secondaries per event and the mean number
